title: GDG San Francisco DevFest 2016 Announced
brief: Devfest is coming to San Francisco!! GDG San Francisco is proud to announce the annual GDG DevFest 2016 which is the biggest crafted by GDG community! The event will take place on **October 8th** in **San Francisco**.

title: Call for Papers Time
brief: Count down to DevFest San Francisco is started! Hurry up and send your talks and sessions while the call for papers is open! [call for talk submissions](https://goo.gl/forms/N7rDDchuhq3iTUhR2).
